<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>I love this site and what it represents as a creative medium; collaborative art is a wonderful thing. I want to see it thrive, and I would love to be able to have a hand in helping it do so. Seminars are a great, unique way to build the site by helping new users along and sharpening their skills. The one I have attended so far was very helpful in learning some of the thought processes behind character and dialogue construction, and I would love to be able to help others like those who lead that seminar helped me. Teaching is something I hope to do as a career at some point; I have volunteer experience with it, and I would love an opportunity to use those and similar skills in the context of this community. Although I'm not the strongest writer myself, I believe I have a good understanding of what works in writing for the site and of the inner workings of articles, and I think I can help newer users with learning these skills.</p>
</div>
