<dl>
<dt><strong>Why do you want to be on JS for Community Outreach (specifically Seminars Team) and why are you a good fit?</strong></dt>
<dd>While I may not be the most renowned of members on the SCP wiki, I've administrated large Discord servers before (sadly, had to delete that Discord account, since I lost my 2FA and backup codes due to a phone reset), so I know how to manage people, and I'm fairly knowledgeable in technical matters, so I think I would have a lot to offer the community in terms of programming/page formatting knowledge.</dd>
<dd><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></dd>
<dd>There are probably many people who are more knowledgeable than me already on this site, but I have the added advantage of generally being able to explain my thoughts in layman's terms so most people can understand me. I think I could be very helpful in teaching many in the community how to format their pages, what kinds of formatting look good, how to create atmosphere with your formatting, etc.</dd>
<dd><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></dd>
<dt><strong>How active are you, both on the site and on the chat?</strong></dt>
<dd>Well, I tend to be very active in the chat, but I'm fairly active on the site as well (or at least the Sandbox, trying to help critique people's works and developing tools for people to use in their writing). I've already made code for a <a href="http://scp-sandbox-3.wikidot.com/jaonhax:obfuscator-demos-and-source">text obfuscator</a>, for example, that I hope people will find useful.</dd>
<dd><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></dd>
<dd>I plan to write articles/tales/canons in the future, and I'm actually <a href="http://scp-sandbox-3.wikidot.com/collab:meska-ekronak-jaonhax">currently working on a medieval canon</a> with <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/meska" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1322433); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1322433&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1591295935" alt="Meska" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1322433)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/meska" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1322433); return false;">Meska</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ekronak" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3409685); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3409685&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1591295935" alt="Ekronak" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3409685)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ekronak" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3409685); return false;">Ekronak</a></span>.</dd>
<dd><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></dd>
<dd>Also, here's a <a href="http://scp-sandbox-3.wikidot.com/jaonhax-demos">Demo page</a> of what I can do with code, in case it helps me get in. Otherwise, just disregard it.</dd>
<dd><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></dd>
